## SLIDE 9 — Feature 6: Intelligence Dashboard (Frontend)
**[Show: the React dashboard — scroll through a briefing card]**

> "All of this is presented through a premium **Intelligence Dashboard** built with React, Vite, and Tailwind CSS.
>
> Each briefing card includes:
> - A **Stability Risk Index** with color-coded severity (green/amber/red).
> - The full **AI-generated report** rendered in rich Markdown.
> - **Key Intelligence Entities** — extracted people, organizations, and locations displayed as interactive chips.
> - A **Media Narrative Landscape** — a visual bias spectrum showing which sources covered the story, categorized as left, center, or right, with direct links to original articles.
> - A **Story Evolution Timeline** — showing how the same narrative has evolved across multiple pipeline runs.
> - **Strategic Impact Analysis** — the AI's assessment of market and security consequences.
> - **Agent Thought Logs** — you can click 'View Intelligence Logs' to see the step-by-step thought process of each AI agent.
>
> The dashboard also includes a **News Copilot** — a chat interface that lets you query the entire knowledge base conversationally."

---

## SLIDE 10 — Feature 7: Dagster Orchestration & Automation
**[Show: the Dagster UI at localhost:3000]**

> "The entire pipeline is orchestrated by **Dagster**, with three main jobs:
>
> 1. `ingest_news_job` — Runs on a bi-daily cron schedule.
> 2. `process_news_job` — Triggered automatically by a sensor when ingestion completes.
> 3. `summarize_news_job` — Triggered automatically by a sensor when processing completes.
>
> This means the system is **fully autonomous**. Once deployed, it ingests, processes, and summarizes global news twice a day — without any human intervention.
>
> Dagster also gives us observability: we can see run history, asset lineage, sensor status, and detailed logs for every step."

---

## SLIDE 11 — Technology Stack Summary
**[Show: a bullet-point slide or table]**

> "To summarize the technology stack:
>
> | Layer | Technology |
> |---|---|
> | Orchestration | Dagster |
> | Ingestion | Python, feedparser, requests |
> | NLP / Embeddings | SentenceTransformer (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) |
> | Clustering | scikit-learn DBSCAN + cosine similarity |
> | Multi-Agent AI | LangGraph (StateGraph) |
> | LLM | Google Gemini (gemini-flash-latest) |
> | Web Search | Tavily API |
> | Database | Supabase PostgreSQL + pgvector |
> | Backend API | FastAPI (for Deep-Dive and Narrative Duel) |
> | Frontend | React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion |
> | Real-Time | Supabase Realtime (WebSocket subscriptions) |
> | Deployment | Docker Compose (6 containers) |"

